name: Moving hand
description:
Fragmented Self-Portraits I by Arianna Tafa

During quarantine of covid-19, I decided to start taking pictures of myself and my surroundings, because it was all I was able to reach back then. As hard to believe as it is, Argentina was/is one of the countries with the hardest restrictions all over the world. That inspired me to show my new tiny world as I lived it. 

2000 x 2000

October 2020.
Buenos Aires, Argentina.
